<div id="review_1781761343" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1781761343" />
    <a title="Alycia Canfield" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/58669532-alycia-canfield"><img alt="Alycia Canfield" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1471287504p2/58669532.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1781761343?book_show_action=true">Oct 11, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Alycia Canfield" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Alycia Canfield" href="/user/show/58669532-alycia-canfield">Alycia Canfield</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/25251770-on-herring-cove-road">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1781761343" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17271000895953404580">Denise the menace in a realistic book., which is what lead me to the book in the first place. I loved it I really did. This is the second in the series and I missed the first, I will go back and read the first but I was okayish with not reading it, however drawn and really want to read it now! The character is warm and its funny, though it is emotional. I love the mix! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


